(48, 1, '2014-01-08 06:28:31', '2014-01-08 06:28:31', 'Mike was born in Hong Kong and educated in England and the United States before returning to Asia to live in 2001. He has more than 15 years experience in the Asian gaming industry, initially establishing new markets for online operator Victor Chandler in South Korea and Malaysia before co-founding SHL with Tim Shepherd in 2004.  Mike directs the corporate strategy and operations of the business from Hong Kong and is a member of the Board of Directors. Mike has a BBA in Finance and Marketing from the Roberto C. Goizueta Business School, at Emory University in Atlanta GA, USA.', 'Mike Bolsover', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mike-bolsover', '', '', '2014-01-08 07:37:12', '2014-01-08 07:37:12', '', 0, 'http://local.silverheritage.com/?post_type=team&#038;p=48', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2014-01-08 06:29:10', '2014-01-08 06:29:10', 'Tim has lived in Hong Kong for 20 years and has more than 15 years experience in the Asian gaming industry. He was a pioneer in launching sports bars in casinos in IndoChina using satellite technology to broadcast odds from the UK.  Tim speaks regularly at international gaming conferences and is an acknowledged expert on emerging Asian gaming markets. Tim has a BSc (Hons) from The City University Business School, London, UK and is a member of the Board of Directors.', 'Tim Shepherd', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tim-shepherd', '', '', '2014-01-08 06:29:10', '2014-01-08 06:29:10', '', 0, 'http://local.silverheritage.com/?post_type=team&#038;p=49', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(50, 1, '2014-01-08 06:29:25', '2014-01-08 06:29:25', 'Paul is a long time Asia resident with more than 35 years of casino management experience which has seen him head up the international operations of Burswood International Resort, Perth, Australia, and the Senior VP Operations at NagaWorld Casino in Phnom Penh, Cambodia following the IPO in 2007.   Paul is based in the company’s regional head office in Vientiane, Laos from where he oversees the group’s experienced casino operations units.', 'Paul Simmons', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'paul-simmons', '', '', '2014-01-08 09:11:26', '2014-01-08 09:11:26', '', 0, 'http://local.silverheritage.com/?post_type=team&#038;p=50', 0, 'team', '', 0),
(51, 1, '2014-01-08 06:29:40', '2014-01-08 06:29:40', 'Martin is a UK Chartered Accountant who has lived and worked in Asia since 1987. He joined SHL in 2006 and brings with him a wide range of financial and operational experience. For 9 years from 2004 to 2013, Martin was an independent non-Executive Director and Chairman of the Audit Committee for Grande Holdings Limited, a company listed on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Martin is a member of the ICAEW and the HKICPA, and has a BSc degree in Electrical &amp; Electronic Engineering from Loughborough University in the UK.', 'Martin Wright', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'martin-wright', '', '', '2014-01-08 06:29:40', '2014-01-08 06:29:40', '', 0, 'http://local.silverheritage.com/?post_type=team&#038;p=51', 0, 'team', '', 0),
